{"tid":545645,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【第37屆金像獎】阿Sa、張繼聰擔任金像獎司儀，宣布茶水蓮姐獲專業精神獎","createTime":"2018-01-30T16:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T02:05:34.000Z","uid":35221,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"848a235f9d5ad04450ccf8abde8d20bff0ca15e8","tid":545645,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:56:35.000Z","msg":"片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/OL.Mingpao/videos/1536505886466247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOL.Mingpao%2Fvideos%2F1536505886466247&d=CEl7%2BMrVAOvvOxzybALzX%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=74b65a20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/OL.Mingpao/videos/1536505886466247</a><br />\n<br />\n【第37屆金像獎】張繼聰蔡卓妍擔任司儀 茶水蓮姐獲專業精神獎 (16:36)<br />\n文章日期：2018年1月30日<br />\n<br />\n《第37屆香港電影金像奬頒奬典禮》即將年4月15日（星期日）晚上，假香港文化中心大劇院舉行，大會今日公佈主持人由張繼聰及蔡卓妍擔任，兩人更接受首個任務，專誠去到這一屆的「專業精神獎」得主楊容蓮（蓮姐）的工作場地探班，並進行拍攝錄影。 <br />\n<br />\n楊容蓮（蓮姐）是第37屆專業精神獎得主，人稱茶水蓮姐，早於80年代已加入電影圈工作，曾參與過百齣電影，一直默默為香港電影幕後工作服務，金像獎協會今次頒發獎項給她，以表揚她為香港電影工業作出專業貢獻，屆時更會在頒獎台上將這榮耀頒發給她。 <br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1517299917459&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1517299917459%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180130&d=CEl7%2BMrVAOvvOxzybALzX%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=f62393ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1517299917459%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180130&h=eca4fc85\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1517299917459&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180130</a>"},{"pid":"54a0791b9ae30f107d79a28961447099eab1e220","tid":545645,"uid":36178,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"阿sa食螺匙食死"},{"pid":"18c6c0eb26894519739d29a96192dfdfa7704d95","tid":545645,"uid":35221,"like":0,"d